Bookshelf Tour Series: https://nebula.tv/videos/thomasflight-my-favorite-film-and-media-books-part-i
Voiceover is one of the most maligned and advised against techniques in film writing, but is does it really deserve such a horrible reputation? In this video I break down some of my favorite examples of voiceover and what separates the great from the truly awful.
